These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bongani, tiparillo, cain
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, coach, freelancer, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, documentary, mystery
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, chess, backgammon
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, pink, apricot, yellow
 1. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing chess##1
 2. the analyst is the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 8. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the freelancer is the cain-smoker##1
10. the person who likes orange is the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
12. the security-guard is the bongani-smoker##1
13. the analyst is in an even position##4
14. the security-guard is the person playing mah-jongg##1
15. the person watching action movies is the bongani-smoker##1
16. the analyst is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
17. the coach is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4        |
| Cigar         | cain    | chaman      | tiparillo | bongani        |
| Job           | freelancer | analyst     | coach     | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | documentary | mystery   | action         |
| Game   | go  | backgammon        | chess   | mah-jongg            |
| Pet           | bird       | chinchilla  | rabbit    | lizard         |
| Color     | orange       | pink     | yellow     | apricot      |

