There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pear, cucumber
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, martial-arts, spy
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, baccarat, ritmeester, alhambra
4 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
City: colone, edinburgh, nizza, san-francisco
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the person eating lettuce is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is the person eating papaya##1
 7. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person eating papaya is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching action movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
13. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3
14. the owner of the mouse is the person watching spy movies##1
15. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
16. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
17. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
18. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
