The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, soccer, volleyball
 1. the security-guard is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the right of the security-guard##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 4. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the librarian is the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the swisher-smoker and the freelancer##2
10. the person drinking milk is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
12. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

