 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the townhouse house and the person eating cucumber##2
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the police-officer##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
10. the doctor is in an even position##4
11. the person eating tomato is the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
14. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
15. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
16. the librarian is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
17. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
18. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1

